              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Bottle",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/5/5d/Bottle.png",
    "type": "Active",
    "quote": "Heart Container",
    "quality": "D",
    "effect": "Holds hearts or ammo for use later.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Upon use, stores an extra pickup.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Using the Bottle again consumes the pickup."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "By using it in a room with a "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Gun Fairy",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", it's possible to capture it.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Using the Bottle with a captured Gun Fairy will spawn a friendly fairy that heals in half-heart increments."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The more health the player has, the faster the healing will be."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "After the player reaches full health and the delay between heals passes, the healing will permanently stop."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "After a few seconds of the fairy orbiting the player, it will disappear. Even if the fairy disappears before the player reaches full health, they will still be healed."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "When playing as "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "The Robot",
              "kind": "character"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "NPCs",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " may give this item to The Robot even if it has not yet been unlocked."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "When playing as The Robot, the friendly fairy will do nothing and will disappear after a while, due to the fact that he has no heart containers."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The item can be used on a health dispenser. If the dispenser holds two half hearts or more, the bottle will store a full heart."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "It is possible to use it in rooms with pickups locked in a cell to avoid opening the door."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Two Bottles can be seen among the pile of items that makes up the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Resourceful Rat",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " throne in the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Resourceful Rat's Lair",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item's ability to catch fairies is a reference to "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "The Legend of Zelda",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Legend_of_Zelda"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The line \"heart container\" is also a reference to the heart containers obtained from bosses in the Legends of Zelda series."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Bomb",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/3/3b/Bomb.png",
    "type": "Active",
    "quote": "Use For Boom",
    "quality": "D",
    "effect": "Throws a bomb that explodes after a short delay.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Throws a bomb onto the ground that explodes after a short delay, dealing 60 damage to nearby enemies."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Triggers an explosion at the position of every enemy on screen."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The bomb's explosion can open "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Secret Rooms",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Bomb can be used to hurt "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Cannonbalrog",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " while it is performing its invulnerable attack."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The Bomb's synergy with the Bow is likely a reference to the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Legend of Zelda series",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Legend_of_Zelda"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ". These two items are staple tools in most of the Zelda games, and the bow in "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Ocarina of Time",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Legend_of_Zelda:_Ocarina_of_Time"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is specifically called the \"Fairy Bow\", as in the synergy name.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "This item's description is also a reference to the Legend of Zelda series, in which secret rooms can be opened with bombs."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The Bomb appears in the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "animated release trailer",
              "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=F07SGMPOO7I"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " for the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Advanced Gungeons & Draguns Update",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Ice Bomb",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/d/de/Ice_Bomb.png",
    "type": "Active",
    "quote": "Cool It!",
    "quality": "D",
    "effect": "Throws a bomb that freezes enemies.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Throws a bomb that deals 8 damage and freezes enemies."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Smart Bombs"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Homing Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " or "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Crutch",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", Ice Bomb will home in on enemies."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Battle Mode"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Orbital Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", creates three bombs which orbit around the player, blocking bullets and exploding in contact with enemies. These bombs won't deal damage to the player, but will knock them back, which could send them into a hazard."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Super Bomberpal"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Lil' Bomber",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", it fires two bombs instead of one, charges twice as fast, and has 20% lower reload time."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Unlike the regular "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Bomb",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", it does not open secret rooms."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This bomb is useless against "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "The Gorgun",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " and will disappear instead of exploding."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If multiple copies of "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Orbital Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " are somehow obtained,  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Battle Mode"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - will spawn three additional bombs for each copy."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Chaff Grenade",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/a/a0/Chaff_Grenade.png",
