              "t": "text",
              "v": " spread Napalm Strike's fire. It can now spread all fire."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The category \"Smells Great!\" in the Ammonomicon is a reference to a quote from the movie "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Apocalypse Now",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", \"I love the smell of napalm in the morning.\""
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Prior to the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "A Farewell to Arms Update",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", Napalm Strike was a  item."
            }
