              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Particulator",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", whenever a split Particulator shot dissipates, a laser is automatically fired in its direction."
