  {
    "name": "Box",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/2/2b/Box.png",
    "type": "Active",
    "quote": "Just A Box",
    "quality": "A",
    "effect": "If the player enters a room while under the box, enemies will not target the player. Firing a weapon will remove the box. Has no effect if used while enemies are already targeting the player. Can be used to steal items from shops.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "While wearing the box, enemies will not target the player. Most actions other than moving will remove the box, including firing a weapon, charging a weapon, dodge rolling, flipping a table, and using teleporters.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Firing a shot while under the box deals double damage and removes the box."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Reloading does not remove the box, even if the player has "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Hip Holster",
                  "kind": "item"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Bosses will not attack the player until they reveal themselves."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Box can be used to "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Stealing",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " from shops as long as it is activated before entering the shop."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Has no effect if used while enemies are already targeting the player."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "While it has no effect on regular bosses as already stated, you can use this to be hidden for the first phase of the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Resourceful Rat",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "’s boss fight."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item is a reference to the famous box disguise from "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Metal Gear",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Metal_Gear"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The synergy  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Pretty Good"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is a reference to the popular quote from Metal Gear Solid, \"You're pretty good\"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The synergy  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Flat Stanley"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is a reference to "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Flat Stanley",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Flat_Stanley"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", an American children's book series written by Jeff Brown."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The synergy  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "What a Thrill!"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is a reference to the theme song of Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The synergy  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Apiary"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " might be a reference to the character The Pain from Metal Gear Solid 3: Snake Eater, a special operative with the ability to control bees and use them in combat."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The synergy  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "I need scissors! 61!"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is a reference to a quote from Metal Gear Solid 2: Sons of Liberty."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Two Boxes can be seen among the pile of items that makes up the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Resourceful Rat",
