              "t": "text",
              "v": " with  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Pulp Gungeon"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", Portable Turret's shots will make the M1911 circling around the player fire.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The effect stacks; if there are multiple Portable Turrets firing at once, the circling M1911 will shoot for each one firing."
