              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Heroine",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", enables Wave Beam mode on Heroine, which fires two wavy projectiles connected by electricity when uncharged, and a standard large Heroine shot when charged. Modes can be switched by reloading Heroine with a full magazine."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Shock Rounds do not electrify water."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The beam damage multiplier granted by Shock Rounds does not stack with the beam damage multipliers of "
            },
            {
