            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Explosive Rounds",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Shadow Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Vorpal Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Blank Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Devolver Rounds",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " or "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Hungry Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The chains of electricity can be used to damage the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Chicken Flute",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " chicken."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The chains of electricity are usually coloured blue, but due to a bug can randomly turn red. In "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Challenge Mode",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", the  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Challenge Mode",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " modifier causes similar electric chains to appear around the room, using the same animation as Shock Rounds'. Once Shockwave has been encountered, Shock Rounds' chains may sometimes appear red, and segments of the Shockwave itself may likewise appear blue."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item is especially effective with piercing bullets, as enemies will be damaged by both the bullets and the electricity between them."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "It is also effective with bouncing bullets, as bullets that miss enemies will create chains of electricity that move across the room and damage enemies."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "trivia": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The name \"Alistair, the Thunderbolt\" is likely a reference to Alastor, both a recurring boss in "
