              "t": "text",
              "v": "Devil May Cry",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ".  In both of his incarnations, he has control over lightning."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "All three of the Void Core weapons, also carried by the Thunderbolt, fire multiple projectiles per trigger-pull, and therefore would always gain this item's benefit."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The sprite of the item resembles a "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Tazie",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", as opposed to "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
