        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Elder Blank Bullets"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player also has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Elder Blank",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", the blank effects reflect all projectiles instead of deleting them."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Blanks triggered by Blank Bullets are affected by Ammolets and causes the short ranged blanks to function strangely. For instance, a blank triggered by Blank Bullets while holding the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Gold Ammolet",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " causes the damaging radius of the blank to affect entire rooms. This phenomenon can also be seen in the mini-blanks generated by "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Clown Mask",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Owl",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", and "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Ser Junkan",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Holy Knight form.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Blank Bullets combined with Gold Ammolet can clear rooms without entering them. Other Ammolets can inflict status effects on enemies before entering the room, but the effect will not progress until the room is entered."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Every projectile fired by the player has a chance to trigger the effect. As such, shotgun type weapons and guns like the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "The Bullet",
              "kind": "character"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " or "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Shell",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " will very frequently trigger the blank effect."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The beam damage multiplier granted by Blank Bullets does not stack with the beam damage multipliers of "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Shock Rounds",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Flak Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Explosive Rounds",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Shadow Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Vorpal Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Katana Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Devolver Rounds",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " or "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Hungry Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If the player has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Gold Junk",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " and "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Ser Junkan",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", every shot from the mech's chain gun will trigger a blank."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The blank effect can open secret rooms, even with an infinite ammo starter weapon or nails launched by "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Casey",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " with the  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Careful Iteration"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "When a blank triggers, it reveals secret rooms anywhere in the current room, regardless of whether it is within the blank's radius."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The chance to fire a blank bullet increases with slow-firing weapons, and decreases with fast-firing weapons.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Despite this, fast firing weapons are generally still vastly superior at triggering the blank effect. For example, the "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Vulcan Cannon",
                  "kind": "gun"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " can reliably trigger the effect every second and sometimes several times per second."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Beam weapons cannot trigger blanks.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Weapons that pierce also cannot trigger blanks unless they hit a wall"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Projectiles created by passive items such as "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Roll Bomb",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " can also trigger blanks."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This cannot activate the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Shrines",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " to spawn a chest, likely because the player could use them to create an infinite number of chests otherwise."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If duplicates of this item are somehow obtained, increases the chance of the bullet-blank effect and allows the item to activate more than once on a bullet."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "trivia": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The tagline is a reference to the well-known adage \"The best defense is a good offense\"."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Orbital Bullets",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/1/19/Orbital_Bullets.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "Deadly Revolution",
    "quality": "A",
    "effect": "Missed shots orbit the player.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The players bullets, after hitting a wall or obstacle, will instantly return to the player and begin to orbit around them for 15 seconds. These orbiting bullets retain all of their special effects.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Bullets orbit at a random distance from the player, between 2 and 5 tiles."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Orbiting bullets no longer collide with walls, but can still collide with "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Enemies",
                  "kind": "unresolved"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " and other world "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Objects",
                  "kind": "unresolved"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " like doors and "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Chests",
                  "kind": "lore"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Only 20 bullets can be in orbit around the player at any time. If this limit is reached, new projectiles will bounce instead of orbiting the player after hitting a wall."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "After the 15 seconds of their orbital lifespan has elapsed, projectiles will fly off of their defined orbit in the direction they were last traveling around the player. These projectiles still do not collide with walls, even after being released from their orbit."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The players beams will start a set distance away from the barrel of their gun, and loop around them once in a perfect circle before traveling straight forward.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Beams that usually bend and wiggle, such as  "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Mega Douser",
                  "kind": "gun"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " or  "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Plunger",
                  "kind": "gun"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": ", will no longer bend."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "If multiple beams are fired at once, each additional beam will begin its circling at a slightly further radius from the player, creating multiple concentric beam circles."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "item_interactions": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Helix Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Instead of orbiting in smooth circles, projectiles will instead follow a rotating elliptical orbit. Instead of traveling in perfect circles around the player, beams will form rotating overlapping shapes with a number of hills and valleys- merging the orbital and helical patterns together.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
