            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "- Because these items/guns are balanced around firing bullets in random directions/away from the aimed direction, being able to direct all of their projectiles towards a single target becomes extremely powerful."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Shadow Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Does not affect additional shadow projectiles."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Prize Pistol",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - The player can use remote bullets to weave their shots around obstacles and hit targets in "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Winchester (NPC)",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " game, allowing skilled players to more easily guarantee a perfect score."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Helix Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Bullets will attempt to follow the player's aim direction, but will still travel in a helical pattern."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Bullets can be curved around cover, allowing the player to attack from a place of safety."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Guns with extremely fast moving projectiles, such as the  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Flash Ray",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", are still affected by this item, but their extreme speed makes guiding their bullets effectively impossible."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "When playing with keyboard and mouse controls, because the players cursor cannot go beyond the bounds of the screen, shooting enemies off-screen becomes nearly impossible."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "With weapons that burst after firing such as the  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Mass Shotgun",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", the effect applies to both parts of the weapon's firing, allowing the player to aim the burst behind the primary projectile."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "A depiction of Remote Bullets can be seen in the opening scroll of the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Supply Drop Trailer",
              "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x3YN0qhy8R8"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Zombie Bullets",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/6/67/Zombie_Bullets.png",
