          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If duplicates of this item are somehow obtained, increases the chance of the effect and allows more ammo to be refunded when shots miss."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Flak Bullets",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/8/80/Flak_Bullets.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "Catch Some!",
    "quality": "C",
    "effect": "Whenever a bullet hits an enemy or wall, it splits into several smaller, lower-damage bullets.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Whenever a bullet hits an enemy or wall, or reaches its maximum range, it splits into several smaller, lower-damage bullets that travel outwards within a limited range. Beams do not split.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "These smaller bullets do not adopt any special properties of the original projectile."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The amount of flak projectiles created is based on the firerate of the original gun, with slower firing guns creating more flak."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The damage and knockback of flak projectiles is equal to the respective stats of the original projectile divided by the number of projectiles created."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The speed of flak projectiles is equal to the speed of the original projectile divided by the number of projectiles, divided by 2."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Doubles the damage of Beam style "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Guns",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "item_interactions": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Bug If two copies of Flak Bullets are obtained through cheats or the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Chests",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", the flak produced by Flak Bullets will split into more flak, which in turn splits into more flak, ad infinitum. These bullets will continue splitting until the game grinds to a halt or crashes."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Casey",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - When swung, Casey will create three tiny high-damage bullets. Enemy bullets batted back by Casey will also break apart into flak."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Boxing Glove",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - When fired, the Boxing Glove will shoot six tiny bullets."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Alien Engine",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Alien Engine will create two tiny bullets for each ammo expended, resulting in a rapid fire stream of flak shots."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Bug  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Face Melter",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Bullets from the Face Melter's amplifier will create flak with a default yellow bullet texture, rather than adopting the appearance of the music notes."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Terminated, Too"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Flak Bullets overrides the effect of this synergy."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Piercing bullets will not split when hitting enemies, but will split when hitting a wall or reaching their maximum range."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The beam damage multiplier granted by Flak Bullets does not stack with the beam damage multipliers of "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Shock Rounds",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Katana Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Explosive Rounds",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Shadow Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Vorpal Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Blank Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Devolver Rounds",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " or "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Hungry Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "A depiction of Flak Bullets can be seen in the opening scroll of the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Supply Drop Trailer",
              "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x3YN0qhy8R8"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
