            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " /  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Stone Dome",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " /  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Zorgun",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " /  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Balloon Gun",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " /  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "The Predator",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " /  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Gunslinger's Ashes",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " /  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Skull Spitter",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - The homing ability of projectiles is "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "not",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " overridden, but is significantly weakened by Helix Bullets."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Bouncy Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - The oscillating direction of helical shots causes them to bounce in unpredictable directions.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
