  {
    "name": "Lichy Trigger Finger",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/1/1c/Lichy_Trigger_Finger.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "Rate of Fire Up",
    "quality": "D",
    "effect": "Increases rate of fire by 25%.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Increases rate of fire by 25%."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Liches Get Stitches"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Riddle of Lead",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", killing an enemy grants a temporary fire rate boost, signified by a green arrow above the player's head like those above enemies buffed by a "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Gunsinger",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If duplicates of this item are somehow obtained, further increases manual fire rate."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "trivia": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The synergy name \"Liches Get Stitches\" is a reference to the phrase \"snitches get stitches\"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The item's name is a play on the phrase \"itchy trigger finger\". A person with said finger is described as eager to fire their weapon or act with haste and no thought put in the action beforehand."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "In "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Dungeons & Dragons",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", a phylactery is a magical item into which a lich binds its soul. As long as its phylactery is intact, a lich cannot be permanently destroyed."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "It may be a reference to Taran Wanderer in which a wizard stores his soul in a finger."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item may be a reference to Roland, a revered Gunslinger from the Dark Tower series."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Lich's Eye Bullets",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/a/a7/Lich%27s_Eye_Bullets.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "Iron Sights",
    "quality": "1S",
    "effect": "Makes all guns act as if they have all their synergies.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Makes all "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Guns",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " act as if they have all of their "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Synergies",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " with other items or guns."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Certain synergies will not be simulated with Lich's Eye Bullets, or have additional requirements for being simulated.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Some two-component synergies that require both guns/items to function, as opposed to one or the other simply being in the player's inventory, will not be simulated. Examples and exceptions include:\n"
                }
              ],
              "sub": [
                {
                  "tokens": [
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": "Dual-wielding synergies such as  "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "synref",
                      "v": "The Submachinist"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": " will not be simulated. However, if a dual-wielding synergy also gives additional benefits, such as with  "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "synref",
                      "v": "Trigger Twins"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": ", the bonuses will still be granted."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "tokens": [
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": " "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "synref",
                      "v": "Rubenstein's Monster"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": " will not be simulated."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "tokens": [
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": "The "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "ref",
                      "v": "38 Special",
                      "kind": "gun"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": "'s  "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "synref",
                      "v": "Detective Mode"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": " synergy would still need the player to acquire the "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "ref",
                      "v": "Badge",
                      "kind": "item"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": " for the policeman to show the contents of chests."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "tokens": [
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": "If the player has "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "ref",
                      "v": "Jolter",
                      "kind": "gun"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": ",  "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "synref",
                      "v": "There Is Only War"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": " will be simulated and the player will have a floating "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "ref",
                      "v": "Demon Head",
                      "kind": "gun"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": " while holding Jolter even if the player does not also have the Demon Head."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Synergies that require 3 or more guns/items will only count Lich's Eye Bullets as "
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "one",
                  "style": "i"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " of the synergy's components, and more will need to be collected for the synergy.\n"
                }
              ],
              "sub": [
                {
                  "tokens": [
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": " "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "synref",
                      "v": "Resourceful Indeed"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": " will only be simulated if "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "ref",
                      "v": "Elimentaler",
                      "kind": "gun"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": " and two of the synergy's other items are acquired."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Synergies that cause guns to transform may override the effects of other synergies. Examples include:\n"
                }
              ],
              "sub": [
                {
                  "tokens": [
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": "With "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "ref",
                      "v": "Big Iron",
                      "kind": "gun"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": ",  "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "synref",
                      "v": "Cast Iron"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": " is overridden by  "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "synref",
                      "v": "Iron Slug"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": "."
                    }
                  ]
                },
                {
                  "tokens": [
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": "With "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "ref",
                      "v": "Lower Case r",
                      "kind": "gun"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": ",  "
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "synref",
                      "v": "Just In Case"
                    },
                    {
                      "t": "text",
                      "v": " overrides all of the gun's other synergies."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "trivia": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Possible reference to Clint Eastwood's \"Deadeye\" as the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Lich",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is the lord over the dead."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Nod to the fact that The Gunslinger & Lich both have bullets as prosthetic eyes.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Due to this, the Gunslinger is unable to drop Lich's Eye Bullets."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Possible reference to Urza's Eyes from Magic: The Gathering; two powerstones acting as the source of his near omnipotence."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item appears on the win screen after defeating the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Lich",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", in a pile of ashes."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Possibly a reference to Acererak the Demilich from "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Dungeons & Dragons",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dungeons_%26_Dragons"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", who has magic soul gems instead of eyes."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Enraging Photo",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/e/e1/Enraging_Photo.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "Don't Believe His Lies",
    "quality": "D",
    "effect": "Taking damage makes the player briefly deal double damage and instantly reloads their weapon.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Upon taking damage, the player gains double "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Damage",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " for 4 seconds."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Upon taking damage, the player's "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Guns",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " will be instantly reloaded."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Cannot be dropped when playing as The Convict."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item will carry over into characters' pasts."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "When found as other Gungeoneers, it cannot be sold to the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Sell Creep",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " or eaten by the serpent."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The man in the picture is "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Black Stache",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", the Past Kill from The Convict's past. He works for the Hegemony of Man, and betrays The Convict at the start of her past."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Ammonomicon",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " quote "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "\"Don't Believe His Lies\"",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is a reference to the film "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Memento",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Memento_(film)"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", in which the protagonist has a polaroid with these words written on it."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Ballot",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/2/20/Ballot.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "Vote Of Confidence!",
    "quality": "C",
    "effect": "Increases the player's coolness by 3, which decreases the cooldown of active items and increases luck.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 3.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Increases "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Coolness",
              "kind": "stat"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " by 3, which decreases the cooldown of active items and increases the chance of items dropping upon clearing a room."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If duplicates of this item are somehow obtained, further increases "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Coolness",
              "kind": "stat"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item being in a gun-themed game is likely a reference to the Abraham Lincoln quote \"The ballot is stronger than the bullet.\"\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "It may also simply be due to the words "
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "ballot",
                  "style": "i"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " and "
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "bullet",
                  "style": "i"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " being near homophones."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Live Ammo",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/b/b1/Live_Ammo.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "I'm A Bullet Too!",
    "quality": "N",
    "effect": "Provides immunity to contact damage, and dodge rolls deal increased damage to enemies.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Grants contact damage immunity.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " This does "
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "not",
                  "style": "i"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " prevent  "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Muzzle Wisp",
                  "kind": "unresolved"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " and  "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Muzzle Flare",
                  "kind": "unresolved"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " from setting the player on fire on contact."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Increases damage dealt by "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Dodge Roll (Move)",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " into enemies by 400% (5x multiplier).\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "For most characters this increases damage dealt per roll from 3 to 15. (15 damage is exactly enough to kill a "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Bullet Kin",
                  "kind": "lore"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " in the "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Keep of the Lead Lord",
                  "kind": "lore"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": ".)"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "As "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "The Robot",
                  "kind": "character"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " stats with innately higher dodge roll damage, Live Ammo instead increases damage dealt per roll from 4 to 20. The Robot can never acquire Live Ammo through natural means, however."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Cannot be dropped."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "item_interactions": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Armor of Thorns",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Roll damage increases stack together multiplicatively, increasing damage per roll to 105 (140 as "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "The Robot",
              "kind": "character"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ")."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Blast Helmet",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Roll damage increases stack together multiplicatively, increasing damage per roll to 45 (60 as "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "The Robot",
              "kind": "character"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ")."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Armor of Thorns",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " +  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Blast Helmet",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - All three items stack together multiplicatively, increasing damage per roll to 315 (420 as "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "The Robot",
              "kind": "character"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ") if all are held.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "This is 105x base dodge roll damage, and surpasses the damage boost given by  "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Ruby Bracelet",
                  "kind": "item"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " in its upgraded form."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item is unique to "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "The Bullet",
              "kind": "character"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " and cannot be acquired by other "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Gungeoneers",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Even with this item, "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Gatling Gull",
