  {
    "name": "Broccoli",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/f/f1/Broccoli.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "Makes You Strong",
    "quality": "A",
    "effect": "Increases damage by 10%, adds a 10% chance to negate damage, and increases movement speed.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Increases damage by 10%."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Adds a 10% chance to negate damage."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Increases movement speed by 1."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Increases health back to full"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If duplicates of this item are somehow obtained, further increases damage, the chance to negate damage, and movement speed."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Prior to the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Supply Drop Update",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", Broccoli was an  item, did not increase speed, and only gave a 5% damage increase."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The Ammonomicon entry for Broccoli is almost identical to the first sentence on the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Wikipedia page for Broccoli",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Broccoli"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", which reads   "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "\"Broccoli",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "is an edible green plant in the ",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "cabbage family",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brassicaceae"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " whose large ",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "flowering head",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pseudanthium"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is eaten as a vegetable.\"",
              "style": "i"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The tagline could be a possible reference to the cartoon character, Popeye the Sailor, who would eat a can of spinach to become stronger."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Crutch",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/4/41/Crutch.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "You Need It",
    "quality": "B",
    "effect": "Causes bullets to slightly curve towards enemies.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "All",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " bullets fired by the player slightly curve towards enemies."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "item_interactions": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Helix Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - The homing ability of projectiles is not overridden, but is significantly weakened by the forced helical motion imparted by Helix Bullets."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The homing of this item appears to stack with guns whose projectiles already home, allowing them to turn faster towards their targets."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Similarly, if duplicates of this item are somehow obtained, bullets home in on enemies more strongly, turning faster to reach their target."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Heavy Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " works well with this item if the player plans to rely on the homing, giving bullets more airtime to home in on enemies."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "A \"crutch\" within multiplayer games usually refers to an item that helps low skill players while hindering high skill players (though usually by opportunity cost); the crutch item does this, as it may curve bullets away from a further high-priority target you were aiming for in favor of arching towards a closer low-threat target."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Pea Cannon"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy is a reference to the game Plants Vs. Zombies Garden Warfare, in which splash damage from the Peashooter class's primary weapon is used as a crutch for aiming. This is a common trope in other games in which a weapon has high splash damage."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Spice",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/9/97/Spice.png",
    "type": "Active",
    "quote": "A tantalizing cube of power.",
    "quality": "A",
    "effect": "Single use. Increases certain stats upon use, depending on how many times it has been used. Each time a spice cube is used, more spice cubes will spawn in place of items or pickups.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If Spice has been used, it has a chance to replace future item drops depending on how many times it has been used."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The effects of spice change depending on how many times it has been used."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "On the first use:\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Adds 1 heart container."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Increases the player's speed by 20%."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Decreases shot spread by 25%."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Increases "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Curse",
                  "kind": "stat"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " by 0.5."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "10% chance for Spice to replace random item drops."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "On the second use:\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Adds 1 heart container."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Slows down enemy bullets by 10%."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Improves firing speed by 20%."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Increases "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Curse",
                  "kind": "stat"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " by 1."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "30% chance for Spice to replace random item drops."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "On the third use:\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Removes 1 heart container."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Slows down enemy bullets by another 5%."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Increases damage by 20%."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Increases "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Curse",
                  "kind": "stat"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " by 1."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "50% chance for Spice to replace random item drops."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "On the fourth and following uses:\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Removes 1 heart container."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Increases damage by 15%."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Increases shot spread by 10%."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Increases "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Curse",
                  "kind": "stat"
                },
                {
