            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " which, when taken, could heighten the user's reaction time to the point where they perceive time in slow motion."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Fear the Old Blood"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Synergy is a reference to the game "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Bloodborne",
              "url": "https://bloodborne.wiki.fextralife.com/Bloodborne+Wiki"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", known for its use of blood vials and \"trick\" weapons. The name of the synergy is an iconic quote from the game."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Tears of Blood"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Synergy is a reference to "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "The Binding of Isaac",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Binding_of_Isaac_(video_game)"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", where several items turn the player's tears into blood."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The internal name of  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Liquid Valkyrie",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is also "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Bloody Eye",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", either in error, or because the item was initially named Bloody Eye early in development."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
