  {
    "name": "Resourceful Sack",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/d/df/Resourceful_Sack.png",
    "type": "Active",
    "quote": "Pack Rat's Rat Pack",
    "quality": "A",
    "effect": "Rolling through bullets collects them in the sack. Using the sack empties the sack and fires a piece of explosive cheese for every bullet collected. Grants 3 extra active item slots.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Rolling through bullets collects them in the sack.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "This effect works even if the Resourceful Sack is not the currently selected item."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The sack holds a maximum of 30 shots，each shot deals 5×2 damage. Additional bullets rolled through will disappear without adding to the total."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "This does not work on bullets fired from turret traps."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Using the sack empties the sack and fires a piece of explosive cheese for every bullet collected. The pieces of cheese "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Status Effects",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " enemies, encasing them in cheese and freezing them. Enemies that die while encheesed spawn a large cheese pool, which encheeses any enemies that step in it."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Grants 3 extra active item slots."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Resourceful Indeed"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player also has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Partially-Eaten Cheese",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Elimentaler",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", and "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Rat Boots",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", the player becomes the Resourceful Rat, preventing items from being stolen when they're left behind in rooms."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The bullets dissipated from the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Bloodied Scarf",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " teleportation ability will not be collected into the sack, nullifying the sack's ability to ever collect bullets while having the scarf equipped."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The sack nullifies "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Rolling Eye",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " and "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Daruma",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " as it collects the bullets before the player rolls through them."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Enemies can be encheesed while in invulnerable states (such as "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Shelleton",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " while turning into a skull), forcing the player to wait until the effect wears off."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item is very useful in Winchester's Game, as the generated bullets can destroy the targets"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
