          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The Iron Coin can be picked up multiple times in the same run. Each Iron Coin obtained gives an additional 3 charges."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The Iron Coin can be used to clear rooms that the "
