  {
    "name": "Wax Wings",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/0/08/Wax_Wings.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "Too Close To The Gun",
    "quality": "B",
    "effect": "Grants flight.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Grants flight, giving the player the ability to fly over "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Pit",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " and floor traps such as spikes.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Flight, by extension, grants immunity to all floor "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Goop",
                  "kind": "lore"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": ", since the player is not actually on the floor to touch it."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Holding the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Dodge Roll (Move)",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " button will instead slow down time. The length of real time that game time can be slowed for is limited, and indicated by a feather-shaped meter in the bottom left of the screen. Slow-motion use-time restores slowly when not in use."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "item_interactions": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Jetpack",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - The player can dodge roll, even while the Jetpack is active. This is largely redundant, however."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Wax Wings utterly trivialise "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Winchester (NPC)",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " shooting gallery, as the player can fly over the pit and shoot every target at point blank range- all but guaranteeing the highest reward."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item is a reference to the Greek legend of "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Icarus",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Icarus"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", where the craftsman Daedalus made wings out of wax and feathers to escape Crete with his son Icarus. However, as Icarus flew too close too the Sun, the wax melted and he fell into the ocean.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Ammonomicon",
                  "kind": "lore"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " quote "
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "\"Too Close To The Gun\"",
                  "style": "i"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " is a reference to Icarus' ultimate fate- flying too close to the "
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "sun",
                  "style": "i"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Cat Bullet King Throne",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/6/63/Cat_Bullet_King_Throne.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "A Cat Throne",
    "quality": "B",
    "effect": "Shoots miniature bullets upon rolling and grants flight.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Grants flight."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Shoots bullets around the player upon dodge rolling. This has a 2-second cooldown.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The bullets benefit from all bullet modifiers."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Mad Cats"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player is holding "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "3rd Party Controller",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " the bullets shot from Cat Bullet King Throne home in on the enemy."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Usurper"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - If the player has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Crown of Guns",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", the Crown appears to fire more rapidly and also makes the Crown automatically charm "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Bullet Kin",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " and "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Veteran Bullet Kin",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " when held."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Bullets are larger while "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "The Scrambler",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is equipped."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "These bullets are affected by Orbital Bullets."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "These bullets can be controlled by "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Remote Bullets",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", which can allow for great amounts of damage."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If the player also has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Jetpack",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", they can dodge roll even while Jetpack is active."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The chance for bullet modifiers to activate is dependent on the gun held."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "When in the Aimless Void, the player retains the ability to shoot bullets by rolling but loses the ability to fly."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Due to it giving flight, the player cannot pet "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Dog",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " while it is equipped."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The bullets can reveal secret rooms.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Bello",
                  "kind": "unresolved"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " ignores the Cat Bullet King Throne firing, even if a bullet makes contact with him, making it useful for finding secret rooms."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The item makes your sprite a few pixels higher than your shadow, and this effect stacks when you have multiple Cat Bullet King Thrones.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "This effect is merely cosmetic however and does not benefit the player in any way."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "You can double the bullets shot by dodge-rolling if you have 2 Cat Bullet King Thrones and so on."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Having Blunderbuss equipped with Blunderbrace synergy grants the synergy effect to Cat Bullet King Throne's bullets."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Blast Helmet",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/b/b3/Blast_Helmet.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "Duck And Cover",
    "quality": "D",
    "effect": "Decreases the radius that explosions will hurt the player in. Grants immunity to contact damage.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Decreases the radius at which explosions can harm the player."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Increases damage dealt by "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Dodge Roll (Move)",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " into enemies by 200% (3x multiplier).\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "For most characters this increases damage dealt per roll from 3 to 9."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "As "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "The Robot",
