              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Armor",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " absorbs one hit regardless of damage, so Lament Configurum can only deal one point of damage at a time to "
