  {
    "name": "Number 2",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/a/a1/Number_2.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "Sidekick No More",
    "quality": "A",
    "effect": "Boosts stats when alone. Only available in co-op, where The Cultist starts with this item.",
    "curse": 0.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Increases the player's "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Movement Speed",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " by 2 (base movement speed is 7) and "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Damage",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " by 41% when their "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Co-op",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " partner is dead. As there is never a co-op partner in singleplayer mode, Number 2 is always active."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Cannot be dropped."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Number 2 was not obtainable in single player until "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "A Farewell to Arms",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "If obtained on any other gungeoneers, it will travel with them into the past."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item isn't required to unlock  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Finished Gun",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Number 2 can drop from  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Rainbow Chest",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " in a "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Rainbow Run",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The icon for this item seems to refer to the Anime \"Afro Samurai\" in which the titular hero wears a "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "similar bandana",
              "url": "http://www.technobuffalo.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/afro-samurai.jpg"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " (standing for \"Number 2\" as in the second highest ranked warrior) while in pursuit to reclaim his father's bandana which is that of the \"Number 1\"."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Number 2 shares its sprite shape with  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Bloodied Scarf",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " and  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Ancient Hero's Bandana",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The damage increase when a co-op partner is dead is 1% higher than the health scaling attributed to co-op mode, thus cancelling out its effects."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "As a base item, before increases such as killing enemies with  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Metronome",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " or carrying Junk with "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "The Robot",
              "kind": "character"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", it is the highest damage increase in the game, surpassing  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Eyepatch",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " by 6%."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
