              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Daruma",
                  "kind": "item"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " - Can be used after dodge rolling over a bullet to trigger a blank effect."
