                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Blank Bullets",
                  "kind": "item"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " - Adds a small chance that any bullet fired will trigger a mini-blank effect upon hitting a wall or enemy."
