              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "\", while a "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "sutra",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sutra"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is a kind of short Indian literary composition intended to teach rituals, literature, philosophy, law, or a great number of other concepts in a brief form, requiring interpretation. Famous examples include the "
