              "v": " - If the player also has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Pulse Cannon",
              "kind": "gun"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " and takes damage, three miniature Pulse Cannons spawn around the player and fire at enemies, before disappearing."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Despite being able to be found in  and  rank chests, it will always have to be bought from a "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Shop",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " at  rank price."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Like all heart container items, "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "The Robot",
              "kind": "character"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " will receive 5 to 10  instead."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Like the other heart container items, the Heart Locket will drop alongside a key if it is found from opening an  rank chest."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "trivia": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Unused and Cut Content/Synergies",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - ("
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "CustomSynergyType.HEART_UNLOCKET",
              "style": "code"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ") If the player has "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Shelleton Key",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", it grants an extra heart container."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The flavor text "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "\"Memento Mori\"",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is a Latin phrase that translates directly into \"Remember Death\" or \"Remember that you will die.\" It is a call to remember that all things must die and to enjoy and be thankful of life."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The item may be a reference to the item of the same name in "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Undertale",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Undertale"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
