                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Fireplace",
                  "kind": "unresolved"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " puzzle entirely."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The Teleporter Prototype will not take the player to a secret room that has already been revealed."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "When the player is teleported into a secret room, the secret wall hiding the room will be immediately opened to reveal the interior."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The Teleporter Prototype "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "cannot",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " teleport the player to the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Resourceful Rat's Lair",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "R&G Dept",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", or "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Bullet Hell",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Using the Teleporter Prototype in a room with enemies will despawn all active enemies and reset the escaped room, similarly to the  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Escape Rope",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "When teleporting into a room containing active enemies, one random enemy in the room will be telefragged in a fountain of blood, dealing 100000 damage."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Cannot",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " be used in the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Resourceful Rat's Lair",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "item_interactions": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Bloodied Scarf",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - Using the Bloodied Scarf, the player can teleport past the invisible barrier at the top of the mysterious eyeball room. This allows the player to walk entirely out of bounds, and wander around the darkness between rooms."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Drill",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " - When taking the player to a random room, the Teleporter Prototype can teleport the player into temporary combat rooms previously created by the drill."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item is based upon the static "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Teleporter",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " used to traverse the chambers of the Gungeon."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Teleporting out of a "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Boss",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " room where the player has already taken damage will "
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "not",
              "style": "i"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " reset the damage taken to the boss, and therefore does not allow the player a second chance to acquire a "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Master Round I",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The Teleporter Prototype will never take the player into a corridor, a "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Boss",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " room itself, entrance or exit elevator rooms, "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Elevator Maintenance Room",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ","
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Second Accident"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " could be a reference to the movie "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "The Fly",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Fly_(1986_film)"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", in which a scientist accidentally combines himself with a fly while attempting to invent a working teleporter. The Shotbow's appearance changes to that of one covered with fleshy growths and a pair of wings, referencing the scientist's later state."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "The  "
            },
            {
              "t": "synref",
              "v": "Telefrag"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " synergy is a reference to a common trope in media with teleporters, where teleporting into a space occupied by another living being kills them."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "Yellow Chamber",
    "icon": "https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/enterthegungeon_gamepedia/images/8/85/Yellow_Chamber.png",
    "type": "Passive",
    "quote": "\"the jammed thing\"",
    "quality": "1S",
    "effect": "Grants 2 heart containers. Upon entering a room, there is a chance that an enemy will be charmed for the duration of the room. Increases fire rate by 15%. Increase curse by 2 while held.",
    "curse": 2.0,
    "coolness": 0.0,
    "wiki": {
      "effects": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Upon entering a room, there is a 60% chance that an enemy will become "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Status Effects",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " for the duration of the room.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Like all charmed enemies, attacks from this enemy can still harm the player."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "When the room is cleared, the enemy charmed by the Yellow Chamber (provided it is still alive) will be briefly "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Stun",
                  "kind": "lore"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " while grey tentacles erupt from the floor and kill it."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "This charmed enemy will not drop  or trigger any on-death effects (such as explosions) if it was killed by these tentacles."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Grants two "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Health",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Increases "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Rate of Fire",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " by 15%."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Increases  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Curse",
              "kind": "stat"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " by 2."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Multiplies the loot weight of the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Battle Standard",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " by 5."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "item_interactions": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Certain "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Companions",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", such as the  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Owl",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ",  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Baby Good Shelleton",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", or  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "R2G2",
              "kind": "item"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " will still attack charmed enemies from the Yellow Chamber."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "notes": [
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Enemies are only charmed in the initial combat wave. Reinforcement enemy waves are unaffected.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "Enemies encountered when using the  "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Lament Configurum",
                  "kind": "item"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": ", a "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Challenge Shrine",
                  "kind": "unresolved"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": ", or the  "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Drill",
                  "kind": "item"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " can be charmed by this item on the first wave of any encounter as normal."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Yellow Chamber will not charm or kill "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Red-Caped Bullet Kin",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "Whenever the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Map (Mechanic)",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " screen is opened, there is a 10% chance for the Yellow chamber to play a special animation in the passive item collection. This animation has a 75% chance to be the chambers of the cylinder blinking, and a 25% chance to be the 'flesh' of the chamber falling away to reveal a single crimson eye beneath. This second animation loops indefinitely with the eye gazing back and forth until the player closes the map."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This item is a reference to the 1895 horror anthology novel "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "The King in Yellow",
              "url": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_King_in_Yellow"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", by Robert W. Chambers.\n"
            }
          ],
          "sub": [
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The item being a chamber is likely a play on the authors name."
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "tokens": [
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "The "
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": "\"single worn glyph\"",
                  "style": "i"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " mentioned in the "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ref",
                  "v": "Ammonomicon",
                  "kind": "lore"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": " description of the Yellow Chamber is likely a reference to the "
                },
                {
                  "t": "ext",
                  "v": "Yellow Sign",
                  "url": "https://lovecraft.fandom.com/wiki/Yellow_Sign"
                },
                {
                  "t": "text",
                  "v": ", a powerful esoteric symbol in several of the short stories in the book."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "This is the only item with a fully lowercase "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Ammonomicon",
              "kind": "lore"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " subtitle."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Bug Charmed enemies will sometimes survive being killed by tentacles on room clear. What causes this is unknown."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Bug Sometimes, if a "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Spent",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " is charmed by the Yellow Chamber and survives to be killed by the tentacles at the end of the room, the doors to the room will unseal while a new wave of Spent spawns."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " Bug If an enemy carrying a  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Balloon!",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": " or  "
            },
            {
              "t": "ref",
              "v": "Replacement Arm",
              "kind": "unresolved"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "  is killed by the tentacles of the Yellow Chamber, the Balloon or Replacement Arm will not drop."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "tokens": [
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": "A depiction of the Yellow Chamber can be seen in the opening scroll of the "
            },
            {
              "t": "ext",
              "v": "Supply Drop Trailer",
              "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x3YN0qhy8R8"
            },
            {
              "t": "text",
              "v": ", each cylinder occupied by a blinking eye."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
